MENTAL HEALTH IS IMPORTANT
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Day before Yesterday's news left everyone shocked and realise the importance of mental health. I admire Sushant Singh Rajput for what he has done, how smart he was. He was a thinker. And if he took such a drastic step you don't what hell he must be going through. You have no idea and you can never feel that. 
Drawing on my personal experiences, I am trying to share how to identify mental health issues and help anyone around u in need. What personally I hate to hear and i love to hear. 
It can be different for person to person. I am no counsellor or a professional, this is just a video based on my personal experience.
Just remember Mental health is very important. You are important. Be kind to others but be kind to yourself first.
Educate yourself before trying to help someone.
